        {
            "title": "江澤民故居向公眾開放  採分段預約制",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"位於江蘇揚州的江澤民故居已向公眾開放參觀。網上圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c5f0baab39c097473960f25b28cea2fc/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250403/_2025040316503561248.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">位於江蘇揚州的江澤民故居已向公眾開放參觀。網上圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>已故領導人江澤民在江蘇揚州的故居，近日向公眾開放。開放採取分段時間預約方式，每周二至周日開放。\n\n</p>\n<p>據新華社報道，3日江澤民故居組織參觀活動，江澤民親屬和生前身邊工作人員代表，江蘇省幹部群眾代表等參加。據悉，江澤民故居於近日面向社會公眾開放。<br/>\n<br/>\n相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3295825/%E6%B1%9F%E6%BE%A4%E6%B0%91%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E6%8F%9A%E5%B7%9E%E6%95%85%E5%B1%85%E7%8F%BE%E8%8A%B1%E6%9D%9F-%E9%9B%84%E9%9B%9E%E5%85%AC%E4%BB%94%E6%90%B6%E7%9C%BC\">江澤民逝世一周年 揚州故居現花束 雄雞公仔搶眼</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"江澤民逝世後，民眾自發到其揚州故居獻花。微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b7e7f364b2bfcf731e3f4573b2217409/2025-04/15_1_28.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        江澤民逝世後，民眾自發到其揚州故居獻花。微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"江澤民逝世後，民眾自發到其揚州故居獻花。微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1b607acd02d676701fd3805b07b9a8c4/2025-04/1130070.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        江澤民逝世後，民眾自發到其揚州故居獻花。微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"江澤民揚州故居向公眾開放。微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b857cc1fef1dc5c775f6fb4ff6d77880/2025-04/1130072.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        江澤民揚州故居向公眾開放。微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"江澤民退休後，曾回揚州故居一遊。微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/04d7960d6bc99ff6fb78b36e036330db/2025-04/1130074.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        江澤民退休後，曾回揚州故居一遊。微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"已故領導人江澤民。新華社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/76084c7edeb8ba4ed3d09d3c80158cb7/2025-04/XI_yaYjommULeXBwErnlFc6grWly8krDUdEZUy_P2VMvz8.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        已故領導人江澤民。新華社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>故居位於江蘇省揚州市廣陵區東關街道東圈門16號，分為東、西兩路院落。西路院落是江澤民童年和青少年時期（1929－1940年）與家人一起租住生活的場所，東路院落為故居基本陳列場所，展陳以江澤民的生平為重點，分為「偉大光輝的一生」、「愛國知識分子家庭」、「揚州永遠是故鄉」三部分。\n\n</p>\n<p>江澤民故居對外開放採取分時段預約方式，每周二至周日開放。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2061934/即時-中國-江澤民故居向公眾開放-採分段預約制",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-03 17:01:31",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "五索馬清鏗公然翹實行街 歌劇院睇騷竟然笑到流眼淚 一行為被外籍人士歧視",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"五索馬清鏗公然翹實行街 歌劇院睇騷竟然笑到流眼淚 一行為被外籍人士歧視\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/d492740ef8b2c5995a0f13279808b788/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250403/_2025040316405689135.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">五索馬清鏗公然翹實行街 歌劇院睇騷竟然笑到流眼淚 一行為被外籍人士歧視</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>已婚大生銀行主席馬清鏗早前被《東周刊》獨家爆出與巨咪網紅「五索」鍾睿心（Rachel）暗交9年就並誕下4名孩子。近日，五索玩高調，頻頻於社交網大晒與馬清鏗去瑞士旅行的甜蜜互動片段，繼獲男方親自餵食後，五索公然翹住馬清鏗行街的畫面曝光。\n\n</p><h2>馬清鏗再次爛鞋</h2>\n<p>五索狂post 瑞士之遊的短片，今次二人去到歌劇院，更坐正第一排，五索晒命表示：「好大鑊，第一排應該個耳膜會聾」；其後，五索就笑言「歌劇院變鬧劇院」，因為馬清鏗的一雙鞋繼日前爛過一次後，再次甩底爛開，馬清鏗在旁無奈表示：「等一陣間要跣返去（酒店）」而五索就笑不停謂：「點解對鞋又出事？（馬清鏗: 有冇橡筋箍啊？) 我冇橡筋喺度喎，你應該問人攞，我幫你拎啊！」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"五索狂post 瑞士之遊的短片，呢日兩人去到歌劇院。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/77993b91489f54e4525658d1c65de785/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-03_at_4_07_51_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        五索狂post 瑞士之遊的短片，呢日兩人去到歌劇院。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"五索與馬清鏗去歌劇院，不過佢就笑到流眼淚。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/db2cdf6a4765eebd3ea97159a6e8ddcf/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-03_at_4_07_51_PM_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        五索與馬清鏗去歌劇院，不過佢就笑到流眼淚。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"因為馬清鏗的鞋繼日前爛過一次後，再次甩底爛開。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0216bc4c50613b4a638686ff405c17f9/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-03_at_4_07_52_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        因為馬清鏗的鞋繼日前爛過一次後，再次甩底爛開。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"五索瘋狂大笑。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6ecc921ab46539eabb1af964fdde8b5b/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-03_at_4_07_53_PM_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        五索瘋狂大笑。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"馬清鏗更問旁邊的女士有冇橡筋箍！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/43daad96f7d62fe30d89c946d39f3780/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-03_at_4_07_51_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        馬清鏗更問旁邊的女士有冇橡筋箍！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"五索公然翹實馬清鏗在街上行。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/03e373f4444d23b8e252816e750bde9d/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-03_at_4_07_52_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        五索公然翹實馬清鏗在街上行。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"兩人首次翹手畫面曝光。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/83ffe72d6b4af2d7eb76729a2038c523/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-03_at_4_07_52_PM_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        兩人首次翹手畫面曝光。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"馬清鏗著住爛鞋跣返酒店。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ad4ecd4b30b620f28057e6f910fc67b9/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-03_at_4_07_53_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        馬清鏗著住爛鞋跣返酒店。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"五索影住馬清鏗著住爛鞋跣步的背影。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b0add6f6548c07f1bbefdc38cd431913/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-03_at_4_07_53_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        五索影住馬清鏗著住爛鞋跣步的背影。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>五索笑到流眼淚</h2>\n<p>五索續指馬清鏗次次在重要時刻對鞋就會爛，買了新鞋又不穿，五索瘋狂地笑，更大爆馬清鏗嘗試用電話叉電線綁住對鞋，「綁嗰陣咁啱比隔籬嗰個女人睇到，佢個樣係極度鄙視我哋啲中國人，著埋啲爛鞋嚟睇歌劇，心諗點解可以有錢坐最前排，個女人個表情真係好正，最好笑係佢（馬清鏗) 仲要問個女人有冇橡筋借俾佢」五索邊說邊笑到流眼淚，而在旁的馬生亦哈哈大笑。\n\n</p><h2>公然翹實馬清鏗</h2>\n<p>完騷後，五索影住馬清鏗小心翼翼逐步跣返酒店，她繼續笑到崩潰，並表示被整條街的人望住，鏡頭一轉，見五索公然翹實馬清鏗在街上行，二人首次翹手畫面曝光。五索更透露二人住總統套房，相當富貴，她影住馬清鏗著住爛鞋跣步的背影，並笑言：「住總統套房嘅客人，返酒店前台嘅鬼佬都歧視佢。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
